casebody.data:
The State of Ohio, Appellee, v. Voorhies, Appellant.

[Cite as State v. Voorhies (1996), 76 Ohio St.3d 132.]

(No. 96-460 — Submitted June 4, 1996 — Decided July 24, 1996.) C. Keith Plummer, Guernsey County Prosecuting Attorney, and Josephine E. Hayes, Assistant Prosecuting Attorney, for appellee. Robert Voorhies, pro se. Per Curiam.

We affirm the judgment of the court of appeals for the reasons stated in its judgment entry.

Judgment affirmed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Stratton, JJ., concur.
